Il parat quil avale les gens
et les transforme en momies.
Il adore manger des lingots dor.

It has been said that they swallow those
who get too close and turn them into
mummies. They like to eat gold nuggets.

Il prend lapparence dun beau cercueil
pour punir les pilleurs de tombes.
Son corps est recouvert dor pur.

They pretend to be elaborate coffins
to teach lessons to grave robbers.
Their bodies are covered in pure gold.

Grave robbers who mistake them
for real coffins and get too close
end up trapped inside their bodies.

On raconte quil ne se souvient dsormais plus

Echnatoll haben einen Krper aus glitzerndem
Gold. Man geht davon aus, dass sie sich nicht
mehr an ihr Leben als Menschen erinnern knnen.

Su cuerpo es de rutilante oro. Se dice que ya no
recuerda nada de su pasado como humano.

ricoperto di oro scintillante. Si dice che ormai

This Pokmon has a body of sparkling gold.
People say it no longer remembers that it was
once human.

On le voit souvent reprsent sur les murs

symbole de leur richesse.

Darstellungen von Echnatoll auf den Wnden
alter Knigsgrber sind ein Zeichen dafr, dass
der dort begrabene Regent wohlhabend war.

Aparece representado en los muros de antiguas

antao.

Viene spesso raffigurato sulle pareti di antichi

There are many depictions of Cofagrigus
decorating ancient tombs. Theyre symbols
of the wealth that kings of bygone eras had.
